title: Transcript: The Democratic debate in Milwaukee, annotated
text: By Team Fix Bernie Sanders and Hillary Clinton are debating in Milwaukee tonight, their second one-on-one debate. It's started at 9 p.m. The Fix team and other Washington Post reporters are using Genius annotations to explain what it all meant.
